XP Investimentos Brokerage Buys Brazil’s Infomoney Website

-- B y   N e y   H a y a s h i
-- 
2011-09-08T14:20:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-08/xp-investimentos-brokerage-buys-brazil-s-infomoney-website.html
XP Investimentos CCTVM SA, a
Brazilian securities broker, agreed to buy online financial
information provider InfoMoney, according to an e-mailed
statement from XP. The brokerage didn’t disclose the amount paid
in the deal.  The purchase of Infomoney will help the brokerage to
increase threefold the number of accounts opened daily within
the next year, according to the statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ney Hayashi in Sao Paulo at 
 ncruz4@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Papadopoulos in New York at 
 papadopoulous@bloomberg.net  